{"id": 1004, "genre": 1001, "title": "婚前你一定要问的问题有哪些？", "description": "讲真，这会儿你脑子里是不是都是“我和你妈掉河里”？（题图来自：Marion Fayolle）", "record_count": 9686, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703181405DIKpSPUgNVOWrX8e.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-05-22T01:00:23Z", "options": [{"id": 80896, "content": "敢不敢去爱尔兰领证？", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618580}, {"id": 80897, "content": "特殊情况下，女方被人侮辱，男方会不会离开她？", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183330YBlNeDx2AiMva4JV.jpg", "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 574264}, {"id": 81153, "content": "会陪我去看不喜欢的电影么", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 619305}, {"id": 80898, "content": "女孩不愿生二胎咋办?", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595124}, {"id": 82434, "content": "说李宇春的加我一个！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615406}, {"id": 80899, "content": "你吃的多么?", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618583}, {"id": 80900, "content": "是不是能沟通，怎么处理情绪", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618585}, {"id": 80901, "content": "出轨了会不会告诉我", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618588}, {"id": 81157, "content": "有无意淫换妻俱乐部！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 394252}, {"id": 80902, "content": "你真的准备好跟我结婚了吗？我的脾气古怪，时好时坏，还特别苛刻。", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 396350}, {"id": 80647, "content": "家里家务谁做？", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 608715}, {"id": 80903, "content": "无聊时谁开启话题和提议做什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 568383}, {"id": 81159, "content": "能做到绝对忠诚么", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 619308}, {"id": 80648, "content": "游戏和我选哪个", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 357524}, {"id": 80904, "content": "我娶你干啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164354}, {"id": 80905, "content": "会陪我一起看李宇春吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611949}, {"id": 80650, "content": "你还是处吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 112, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229995}, {"id": 80906, "content": "我爱他／她吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618595}, {"id": 80651, "content": "婚姻比任何都难经营。年轻人要真懂了未必会结婚吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617439}, {"id": 80907, "content": "我爱他／她吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618595}, {"id": 81419, "content": "婚后还能自由生活。有事互相商量，互相帮助。有争议的事暂且搁置", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620291}, {"id": 80652, "content": "你是哪个星座", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617446}, {"id": 80908, "content": "你能做到疼我一辈子吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347040}, {"id": 80910, "content": "你愿意疼我一辈子吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347040}, {"id": 80655, "content": "和自己住？还是父母住", "image": null, "praise_count": 68, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595927}, {"id": 80911, "content": "爱我为什么不给我一分钱面包？", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593592}, {"id": 80656, "content": "一般谁烧饭谁洗碗", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469244}, {"id": 80912, "content": "你爱我吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419167}, {"id": 80657, "content": "喜不喜欢孩子？", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617727}, {"id": 80913, "content": "\n对将来有什么想法？", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419167}, {"id": 80658, "content": "因为爱我而结婚还是只是因为合适", "image": null, "praise_count": 107, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617764}, {"id": 80914, "content": "过年先回谁家？", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602876}, {"id": 81426, "content": "不知道呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620325}, {"id": 82451, "content": "到底是先有爱还是先有情？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 624485}, {"id": 80660, "content": "看不看好奇心日报", "image": null, "praise_count": 99, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578664}, {"id": 80916, "content": "喜不喜欢赵寅成", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423267}, {"id": 80661, "content": "我们在一起你快乐吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617781}, {"id": 80917, "content": "会尊重我吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419167}, {"id": 80662, "content": "为什么要和我结婚？", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 612048}, {"id": 80918, "content": "你会不会管我挣多少用多少？", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 257441}, {"id": 80663, "content": "如果结婚后，你再遇见了爱的人。一定要告诉我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 223, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590885}, {"id": 80919, "content": "我能不给你打辅助吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618602}, {"id": 80664, "content": "跟不跟父母一起住", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615316}, {"id": 80920, "content": "我是不是还能做我自己？不道德绑架，不勉强我做不愿意做的事情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488298}, {"id": 80665, "content": "两个人在完美结合，是因为爱，如果婚后感情没了，请向对方坦白", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589987}, {"id": 80921, "content": "谁烧饭？", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254315}, {"id": 80666, "content": "生孩子保大人保孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 109, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598731}, {"id": 80922, "content": "愿意将你一生托福给我吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618605}, {"id": 80667, "content": "?", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617809}, {"id": 80923, "content": "礼金是多少？", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598905}]}